Cutting edge opportunity for developers

Hi Brian, 

I hope you're having a great week. I'm a recruiter here at Willis Towers Watson working directly with our development team and we would be interested in talking to you about a couple open engineer spots on our team. We're a growing team in a brand new building here in Tempe. We have great perks on the team but most importantly we work with a lot of different technologies and SOLID-minded developers. We feel there's a lot of opportunity to grow as a developer and cultivate our strengths and weaknesses. We're geared towards C# and React JS with a lot of other tech we utilize.

Could you let me know if this would be interesting to you at the moment, or if there is anyone else in your network who could be a good fit? 

Thanks for your time!

Regards,

Chase Leslie
chase.leslie@extendhealth.com
480-401-3535
What is the most important question you have for me?

Hey – thank you for the add Brian! The most important question I would ask is what are you looking to achieve or build in your career?

If you have a good phone number it’d be great to have a brief call, let me know what you think!


Chase Leslie
Recruiter, Exchange Solutions

Willis Towers Watson
Email: chase.leslie@extendhealth.com<mailto:chase.leslie@extendhealth.com>
Office: + 1 480 401 3535

www.medicare.oneexchange.com/careers<http://www.medicare.oneexchange.com/careers>
